140 chars, ENG, web+AI:

Since I have followed the evolution of the triad JS+HTML+CSS from the beginning, I have always been very sound of them in their pure form; I would even rather create my own JS frameworks instead of using ready-mades. On the flip side, more than a web designer, I am a researcher of tech science and creativity - which supports a great interest in AI and its recent advancements.

